Yes, Bernie Madoff was a criminal. Madoff was an American financier who was the mastermind behind a Ponzi scheme that defrauded thousands of people out of billions of dollars. He founded Bernard L. Madoff Investment Securities LLC and used it to run one of the largest financial frauds in history. In 2009, Madoff was arrested and later pleaded guilty to 11 counts of fraud, money laundering, and other crimes. He was sentenced to 150 years in prison, and he died in prison in 2021.